snippet.title: Star Knight: Order of the Vortex - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Choose your ship, build your crew, and enter the Vortex...

Star Knight: Order of the Vortex is an upcoming roguelite, shoot-em-up for PC. Play as a member of the Order of the Vortex, a Star Knight tasked with defending the human kingdoms from the terrors that lie within the Vortex.

Wishlist now on Steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2462090/Star_Knight_Order_of_the_Vortex/

Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/rv3jWbVQfG

Play the current version for free on itch.io: 
https://eagleofbrittany.itch.io/starknight
